summary: This document is an Assignment of Lease and Consent to Assignment dated July 10, 2025, involving Allurion Technologies, Inc. (Assignor), Aila Technologies, Inc. (Assignee), and 3 Huron Investments, LLC (Landlord). It details the transfer of lease obligations from Assignor to Assignee, effective September 1, 2025, with Landlord's consent, and includes provisions regarding security deposits and the condition of the premises. The Assignor remains liable for past and future obligations under the lease.
